// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1569 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 1b1d3545-451e-5ba5-a416-d86c353b9c5a

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
